          <li>We are not liable for pre-existing health conditions or behavioral issues</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section id="owner-insurance">
        <h3>9.3 Pet Owner Insurance</h3>
        <p>
          We strongly recommend you maintain appropriate pet insurance to cover veterinary costs and third-party liability.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="exclusions">
        <h3>9.4 Exclusions</h3>
        <p>We are not liable for:</p>
