    </section>

    <hr class="my-8" />

    <section id="data-protection">
      <h2>10. Data Protection and Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        We are committed to protecting your privacy in accordance with UK GDPR and the Data Protection Act 2018. 
        Our full <a href="/privacy" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Privacy Policy</a> is available on our 
        website and governs how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.
