          <li>Contact and booking information</li>
          <li>Pet health and care details</li>
          <li>Photos and videos for service updates</li>
          <li>Payment information (processed by third-party providers)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section id="info-use">
        <h3>10.2 Use of Information</h3>
        <p>Your information is used only for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Providing our Services</li>
          <li>Communication regarding your booking</li>
          <li>Emergency situations</li>
          <li>Legal compliance</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </section>

    <hr class="my-8" />

    <section id="intellectual-property">
      <h2>11. Intellectual Property</h2>

      <section id="content-ownership">
        <h3>11.1 Content Ownership</h3>
        <p>
          All photos, videos, and content created during our Services remain our property but may be shared with 
          you for personal use.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="marketing-use">
        <h3>11.2 Marketing Use</h3>
        <p>
          You consent to our use of non-identifying photos and testimonials for marketing purposes unless you 
          specifically opt out.
        </p>
      </section>
    </section>

    <hr class="my-8" />

    <section id="termination">
      <h2>12. Termination</h2>

      <section id="owner-termination">
        <h3>12.1 Termination by Pet Owner</h3>
        <p>
          You may terminate our Services at any time with appropriate notice according to our cancellation policy.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="maau-termination">
        <h3>12.2 Termination by Maau Maau</h3>
