        <ul>
          <li>Terms and Conditions are breached</li>
          <li>Payment is not received</li>
          <li>Safety of our staff or other animals is at risk</li>
          <li>False information is provided</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </section>

    <hr class="my-8" />

    <section id="complaints">
      <h2>13. Complaints and Disputes</h2>

      <section id="complaint-process">
        <h3>13.1 Complaint Process</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Contact us within 48 hours of any concern</li>
          <li>We will investigate and respond within 5 business days</li>
          <li>Formal complaints should be submitted in writing</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section id="resolution">
        <h3>13.2 Resolution</h3>
        <p>We are committed to resolving all disputes fairly and may offer:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Service credits</li>
          <li>Partial refunds</li>
          <li>Additional services at no charge</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </section>

    <hr class="my-8" />

    <section id="governing-law">
      <h2>14. Governing Law</h2>
      <p>
        These Terms are governed by English law. Any disputes will be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of 
